<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title><% title %></title>
	<!--Import Google Icon Font-->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Import Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="font-awesome-4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <!--Import materialize.css-->
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/materialize.min.css"  media="screen,projection"/>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="stylesheets/style.css">

    <!--Let browser know website is optimized for mobile-->
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>

    <!--Import jQuery before materialize.js-->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="javascript/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="javascript/materialize.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<nav class="grey darken-4" role="navigation">
		<div class="nav-wrapper container">
			<a id="logo-container" href="/" class="brand-logo">
				<i class="fa fa-btc fa-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
				<i class="fa fa-arrows-h" aria-hidden="true"></i>
				SHM
			</a>
		  <ul class="right hide-on-med-and-down">
		    <li><a class="toggle-login">Log In</a></li>
		  </ul>

		  <ul id="nav-mobile" class="side-nav">
		    <li><a class="toggle-login">Log In</a></li>
		  </ul>
		  <a href="#" data-activates="nav-mobile" class="button-collapse"><i class="material-icons">menu</i></a>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<!-- change background color of the header -->
	<div class="teal darken-4">

		<!-- HEADER -->
		<div class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="heading">
					<div class="center-align white-text">
						<h1 class="header center"><%= title %></h1>
						<p>The only interdimensional crypto exchange that trades schmeckles for bitcoins!
						</p>
						<p>Scroll to learn more or whatever.</p>
						<br>	
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col s5 right-align">
							<a href="/register" class="waves-effect waves-light amber darken-3 btn">Register</a>
						</div>	
						<div class="col s2 center-align">
							<a class="waves-effect waves-light  amber darken-3 btn toggle-login">Log In</a>
						</div>	
						<div class="col s5 left-align">
							<a class="waves-effect waves-light amber darken-3 btn scroll-about">About Us</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div> <!-- end color div for header -->


	<!-- COLOR FOR LOGIN AND NEWS -->
	<div class="cyan lighten-5">

		<!-- LOGIN FORM (HIDDEN UNTIL CLICK) -->
		<div class="hidden" id="login-form">
			<div class="section">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col s2 m3 l4"></div>
						<div class="col s10 m6 l4">
							<div class="card grey lighten-5">
								<div class="card-content">
									<span class="card-title">Log In <a><i class="material-icons right tiny black-text toggle-login">close</i></a></span>
									<div class="row">
										<div class="input-field col s6">
											<input placeholder="Username" id="user_name" type="text" class="validate">
										</div>
										<div class="input-field col s6">
											<input placeholder="Password" id="password" type="text" class="validate">
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="card-action">
									<a href="/" class="teal-text">Submit</a>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col s2 m3 l4"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<br/>

		<!-- NEWS AND USER TESTIMONIALS -->
		<div id="news-testimonials">
		<div class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col s12 m6 left-align padded-column">
						<h3 class="header">Recent News</h3>

						<div class="card horizontal teal darken-2 white-text z-depth-3">
							<div class="card-image white">
								<img src="images/bar.png">
							</div>
							<div class="card-stacked">
								<div class="card-content">
									<span class="card-title">Strength of Schmeckle Rebounds</span>
									<p>
										The destruction of the Citadel caused a drop in Schmeckle value and a rise in BTC value, as many experts predicted. Now the Schmeckle is gaining traction once again - but is this increase a lasting trend, and will SHM reach parity with its previous value?
									</p>
								</div>
								<div class="card-action">
									<a href="#">Read More</a>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="card horizontal cyan darken-4 white-text z-depth-3">
							<div class="card-image grey lighten-5">
								<img src="images/presidentmorty.jpg">
							</div>
							<div class="card-stacked">
								<div class="card-content">
									<span class="card-title">Will BTC Be Affected by a Morty Presidency?</span>
									<p>
										BTC has experienced increased volatility following the unexpected election of a Morty to lead the Citadel. Investors are unsure if the price of BTC will maintain its current trends, especially given the rumors surrounding Morty's willingness to impose new cryptocurrency regulations. 
									</p>
								</div>
								<div class="card-action">
									<a href="#">Read More</a>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

					</div> <!-- end recent news -->

<!-- 					<div class="col s0 m1"></div>
 -->

					<div class="col s12 m6 right-align padded-column">
						<h3 class="header">User Testimonials</h3>

						<div class="card horizontal teal darken-2 white-text z-depth-3">
							<div class="card-image grey lighten-5">
								<img src="images/Rick_Sanchez.png">
							</div>
							<div class="card-stacked">
								<div class="card-content">
									<span class="card-title">Rick C-137</span>
									<p>
										"Yeah, MtSchmex is pretty good, I guess. I use it to shuffle around my assets because no currency is immune to *burrrp* crashing or disappearing from reality."
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="card horizontal cyan darken-4 white-text z-depth-3">
							<div class="card-image grey lighten-5">
								<img src="images/mr_pbh.jpg">
							</div>
							<div class="card-stacked">
								<div class="card-content">
									<span class="card-title">Mr. PBH</span>
									<p>
										"Ooooo wee, MtSchmex is pretty great!"
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="card horizontal teal darken-2 white-text z-depth-3">
							<div class="card-image grey lighten-5">
								<img src="images/ants.jpg">
							</div>
							<div class="card-stacked">
								<div class="card-content">
									<span class="card-title">"Ants In My Eyes" Johnson</span>
									<p>
										"I can't see anything! It's all ants!!"
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div> <!-- end testimonials -->

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		</div>

	</div> <!-- end color div for login and news/testimonials -->

	<div class="cyan darken-4 white-text">
		
		<!-- ABOUT -->
		<div class="container">
		<div class="section about">

			<div class="row">
				<div class="col s12">
					<h3 class="heading center-align">About Us</h3>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col s0 m2 l3"></div>
				<div class="col s12 m8 l6">
					<p class="center-align light" style="font-size: 1.2em">
						MtSchmex trades your schmeckles for bitcoins, and sometimes the other way around. We also offer several interdimensional altcoins such as Kronencoin, Plumbuscoin and Noobulum! Open an account today to see what we got, man!
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col s0 m2 l3"></div>
			</div>

			<br>

			<!-- info icons --> 
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col s12 m4">
		          <div class="icon-block">
		            <h2 class="center amber-text text-accent-3"><i class="material-icons small">credit_card</i></h2>
		            <h5 class="center">Put Money on a Card</h5>

		            <p class="light center-align">We offer instant transfers to and from a variety of plastic electronic money card vendors.</p>
		          </div>
		        </div>

		        <div class="col s12 m4">
		          <div class="icon-block">
		            <h2 class="center amber-text text-accent-3"><i class="material-icons small">lock</i></h2>
		            <h5 class="center">Lots of Security</h5>

		            <p class="light center-align">We use top-of-the-line quantum dimensional cryptography standards. Your schmeckles are safe with us.</p>
		          </div>
		        </div>

		        <div class="col s12 m4">
		          <div class="icon-block">
		            <h2 class="center amber-text text-accent-3"><i class="material-icons small">network_check</i></h2>
		            <h5 class="center">Interdimensional Signal</h5>

		            <p class="light center-align">Taking a trip to another dimension? No problem. You'll still be able to deposit and withdraw from wherever you end up.</p>
		          </div>
		        </div>
			</div>
		</div>
		</div>

	</div> <!-- end color div for About -->

	<footer class="page-footer teal darken-2">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
			<div class="col s0 m2"></div>
				<div class="col s12 m4 center-align">
					<h3 class="header">Contact</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<i class="fa fa-envelope fa-lg padded-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i> <a class="white-text" href="mailto:admin@mtschmex.io">admin@mtschmex.io</a>
						</li>
						<li><p> </p></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="col s12 m4 center-align">
					<h3 class="header">Source Code</h3>
					<p>View our source on Github!</p>
					<p><i class="fa fa-github fa-lg padded-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i> <a target="_blank" class="white-text" href="https://www.github.com/ewmiller/mtschmex">github.com/ewmiller/mtschmex</a></p>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-copyright">
	      <div class="container center-align">
	      	<i class="fa fa-copyright fa-lg padded-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i> Ethan Miller | 2017
	      </div>
    </div>
	</footer>



	<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8" async defer>
		$(document).ready(function(){
			$(".toggle-login").click(function(){
				$("#login-form").slideToggle();
			});
			$(".scroll-about").click(function(){
				$('html, body').animate({
					scrollTop: $(".about").offset().top
				}, 1000);
			});
		});
	</script>

</body>
</html>